column8: Partly cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers in the south, slight (30%) chance elsewhere. Snow possible above 1100 metres. Winds southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h. Daytime maximum temperatures between 8 and 18.

Partly cloudy. Slight (20%) chance of a shower. Snow possible above 1200 metres. Winds southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h. Overnight temperatures falling to between 3 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching between 9 and 19.

Cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower. Snow possible above 1400 metres. Winds southeasterly 15 to 25 km/h becoming light during the morning. Overnight temperatures falling to between 4 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching between 11 and 19.

Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog in the north. Medium (60%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm in the late morning and afternoon. Light winds. Overnight temperatures falling to around 6 with daytime temperatures reaching between 15 and 22.
